<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-20195] CQL single file doc page has obsolete and invalid markup</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-20195</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&quot;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/developing/cql/cql_singlefile.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;cql_singlefile.html&lt;/a&gt; has invalid markup. The legacy markup in the file resembles Wiki Markup.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Old markup requiring conversion:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;bc(syntax) to &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;source, bnf&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;bc(sample) to &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;source, sql&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;p. indicates end of code block, to four dashes (----)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;code in AsciiDoc doesn&apos;t require escaping curly bracket&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;back quotes in code changed to regular single quotes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&apos;sql&apos;, &apos;bnf&apos; and &apos;text&apos; are source language names supported in AsciiDocs Pygments highlighter.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example, invalid formatting in &lt;a href=&quot;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/developing/cql/cql_singlefile.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;cql_singlefile.html&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13073862/13073862_image-2025-01-08-13-26-48-829.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Correct formatting of same content on DDL (&lt;a href=&quot;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/developing/cql/ddl.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;ddl.html&lt;/a&gt;) page:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13073863/13073863_image-2025-01-08-13-25-42-002.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
